{"prompt": "Generate a website for a health and wellness app. The website should be artistic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Vitality Haven</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #E53935; /* Red */\n            --secondary-color: #FFCDD2; /* Lighter shade of red */\n            --text-color: #212121;\n            --background-color: #FFFFFF;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            color: #FFFFFF;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        .hero-wave {\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: -50px;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            transform: rotate(180deg);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 60px auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        .features {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 40px;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n        }\n\n        .cta h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .cta p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto 30px auto;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: #FFFFFF;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            border-radius: 50px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #D32F2F; /* Darker red */\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            background-color: #F5F5F5;\n            color: #757575;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        /* Basic SVG wave for visual appeal */\n        svg {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100px; /* Adjust height as needed */\n            display: block;\n        }\n\n        .wave-path {\n            fill: #FFFFFF; /* To blend with the background */\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Vitality Haven</h1>\n        <p>Nourish your body, calm your mind, and empower your spirit. Your journey to holistic well-being starts here.</p>\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1440 320\" class=\"hero-wave\">\n            <path class=\"wave-path\" fill=\"#ffffff\" fill-opacity=\"1\" d=\"M0,160L80.7,170.7C161.3,181,323,203,485,197.3C647.3,192,809,160,965,133.3C1121.3,107,1283,85,1364,74.7L1440,64L1440,320L1364,320C1283,320,1121.3,320,965,320C809,320,647.3,320,485,320C323,320,161.3,320,80.7,320L0,320Z\"></path>\n        </svg>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Discover Your Inner Balance</h2>\n        <div class=\"features\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-seedling\"></i>\n                <h3>Mindful Movement</h3>\n                <p>Engage in guided yoga and meditation sessions designed to reduce stress and increase flexibility.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-heartbeat\"></i>\n                <h3>Personalized Nutrition</h3>\n                <p>Receive tailored meal plans and recipes based on your health goals and dietary preferences.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-book-open\"></i>\n                <h3>Holistic Learning</h3>\n                <p>Access a library of articles, workshops, and expert advice on mental and physical wellness.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <section class=\"cta\">\n        <h2>Ready to Transform Your Life?</h2>\n        <p>Join Vitality Haven today and embark on a journey towards a healthier, happier you.</p>\n        <a href=\"#download\" class=\"cta-button\">Download the App</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Vitality Haven. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}